title Submitting a note (SPA)

user->browser: some text is written into the text field and the submit button is clicked

note over browser:
the onsubmit event is triggered
and a new note is created
and appended to the note list
of the html document
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa

note over server:
server responses with 201 created
and a response text
end note

server-->browser: Status code 201 created {"message":"note created"}
